               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the donor and scribe.&#xD;
Groups of lines, alternating with black lines, in the incipit page of Text I and in the incipit of Text II; the beginning of some paragraphs in Text I (s. fols. 1ra, 2ra); the words sälam and Ṣadəqan (ʾo-Ṣadəqan) in Text II.&#xD;
Some corrections interlineally and lines marking erasures; elements of the punctuation signs and of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
